*FOR FILE CODE PLACEMENT*

FIRST MAKE SURE TO ENABLE API SERVICES!!!!

DATA STORE CODE NEEDS TO BE IN SERVERSCRIPT SERVICE AND THE SCRIPT SHOULD BE CALLED "DataStore".

OPEN CLOSE SHOP CODE SHOULD BE IN A LOCALSCRIPT IN STARTERGUI, THE SCRIPT CAN REALLY BE CALLED ANYTHING.

BUYINGITEMS CODE SHOULD BE PUT IN A SERVERSCRIPT IN SERVERSCRIPTSERVICE AND ALSO CAN BE CALLED WHATEVER YOU WANT.

IN REPLICATEDSTORAGE A FOLDER SHOULD BE MADE CALLED "ShopEvents" AND INSIDE THERE SHOULD BE THREE REMOTE EVENTS ONE CALLED "Sword" ANOTHER CALLED "Gun" AND A LAST ONE CALLED "FlashLight".

FROM THE TOOLBOX CLASSICSWORD, FLASH LIGHT AND HYPERLASERGUN SHOULD BE IMPORTED.

4 PARTS SHOULD BE CREATED ONE CALLED "CamPart" THE SECOND ONE CALLED "CamPart1" THE THIRD ONE CALLED "CamPart2" THE LAST ONE CALLED "ShopCam".

ANOTHER PART SHOULD BE CALLED "OpenShop".
